Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大總統回來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像他在正門破壞了布里克斯的戰車
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活該
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里克斯的山猴子們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合剩下的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奪回作戰本部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大總統在正門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是第一次見到本人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扯斷我孫女手臂的人 是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}永遠的休假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犧牲一般人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些高官獲得長生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,統一世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德雷大總統也是明白真相還在繼續的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是為了這個目的而生的國家領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼好猶豫的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了製造沒有戰爭的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了那個就要毀滅一次嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是毀滅 是再生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你們鍊金術師說的再構築
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶給一般國民的不是死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在我們的體內獲取永生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後一起統一世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一是全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們亞美斯多利斯被選中的人 將成為一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們準備怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們想獨吞好處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼放著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你們跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話 就向那位大人說些好話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能遵從長官的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經不知道該相信誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了這個份上還能猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使跟從不能信任的長官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不能說是忠誠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是自我欺瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選擇不會讓自己的靈魂蒙羞的活法就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城裡有我家人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准將閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我們的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰本部 情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各處的中央兵都活過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閣下現在何處？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大總統辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生存者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和辦公室周圍的我方人員無法取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡被中央兵包圍的可能性很大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你們那裡有危險就逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捨棄我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡又到處是敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央兵整理隊形衝進這裡也只是時間問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下降到一定程度後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和來的時候一樣 挖個逃脫用的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:05:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃脫？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也需要時間調整態勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然這麼想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們能通過氣息知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不詳的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手臂被取走的舊傷隱隱作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀哦呀 沒想到會有觀眾來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是製造了金格·布拉德雷的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製作了大總統…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說 你是那邊的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以為你在廣播局 沒想到專程親自來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省了我不少事真謝謝你 馬斯坦古君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們稍微陪他們玩會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:07:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人偶兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 和那個動作明顯不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是可能會成為金格·布拉德雷的男人們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出生後立刻被集中起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為大總統
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是為了這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在專門的教育和訓練中成長的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 第12次實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金格·布拉德雷誕生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這些人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 他們一直積累著戰鬥經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然比不上金格·布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 該死的叛亂軍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 暈過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔掉反而會失血過多而死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危險的 大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並非故意…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然這種武器感覺很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明比我年紀還大 動作倒是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爺 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清國的皇子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子 麟…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擅自出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前切斷手臂的女孩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又這樣為了無法捨棄的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓自己的生命處於危險的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快快扔了我這種無法戰鬥的老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我變得和那個男人一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王是為了人民而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人民就不存在王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要捨棄自己國家的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我所追求的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不適合做王的男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可必須要打倒才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說了 休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休假…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要一次休假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:11:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快硬化 古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護少主的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 成為王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這老頭子 要在這裡永遠地休假了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起去地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賭上這條命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒法傷他一毫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真沒臉見您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使有著神一般的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從看不見的地方來的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是沒有辦法躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通向地獄的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 萬分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一會掉水溝 一會撞路燈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你駕駛水平真差 小鬍子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦 用那破車能到這裡就謝天謝地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到這裡了 還吵什麼架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 快點找到進入地下的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是馬斯坦古大佐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進行得順利就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超出常人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也該有個限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你背後全空了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有放心交付的部下 所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理之門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鍊金術的禁忌人體鍊成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘗試它的術師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是打開過真理之門的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然要支付相應的通行費
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:16:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛力克兄弟犧牲了自己身體的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面被拿走了一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 做到這個程度所明白的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是人體鍊成 不會成功而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 這種話題軍人沒興趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.26,0:16:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打開過真理之門的人就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們所說的人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定能成為瞭解敵人企圖的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜打開真理之門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜犧牲自己的肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想再次見面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你們心裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論花多少代價
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想再見一次的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是和軍人無緣的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對死人的依戀沒有任何意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有為了不讓他們死而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛德華·愛力克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威脅他說出所知道的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那青梅竹馬被當成了人質的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他卻一點都沒有透露
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是說了一句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請理解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那眼神和我們軍人的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及被稱為軍隊走狗的鍊金術師的眼神不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不能再失去什麼重要東西的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不聽勸告的小孩子的眼神？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果說沒有被那直白的眼神打動的話 那是謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那可以說是愚昧的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果能在這場戰鬥中殺開活路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 差不多該開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,16號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,17號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,21號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,23號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,26號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 這只是第一階段
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道這中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有幾個大總統直轄的鍊金術研究所嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在所使用的是市內4處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五研究所？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5個頂點的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鍊成陣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道 那個弧形的地下道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畫著連接研究所的圓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 亨克爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茲米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來這裡剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用這牆壁挖個逃脫用的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離我遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就在這裡分別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還不得不留在這裡戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下面恐怕是敵人的中樞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放過奇襲的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受妳照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 伊茲米·卡迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才該謝謝您 阿姆斯壯少將
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾馮斯君？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:21:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茲米？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊茲米
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼 鋼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,憤怒產於悲傷之絕境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個靈魂寄宿於同一個身體
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.34,0:24:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,開始殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.33,0:24:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.06,0:24:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第58話 人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.87,0:24:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使死去也要繼續保護
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.22,0:24:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是本願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:07.24,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}終於找到了  全新的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:11.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}日月卻來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:16.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}我前往的地方  不是「未來」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:20.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}僅僅不停地追趕著「過去」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:27.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}不停地鳴響著 那過去的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:31.14,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}彷彿無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:36.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}差不多了吧  那厭倦搜索的臉龐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:41.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}丟掉心裡的糾結
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:46.85,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  總有會停的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:52.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}這麼漫長  卻如此冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:57.39,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  為什麼會選擇我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:01:02.14,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}籠罩著我  真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:06.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  已經忘了停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:12.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天依然持續下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:17.22,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在默默撐開的雨傘下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.71,0:01:28.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}接近那溫暖的懷抱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:41.92,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}從那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:46.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}就決定不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:51.71,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}即使承擔再多的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.71,0:22:56.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仍有無法原諒的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:00.27,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已經無法回到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:02.82,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.82,0:23:07.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我還沒有做成任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:13.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的記憶之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.11,0:23:18.97,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}又有一塊  消逝而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.65,0:23:21.99,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回望今日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.99,0:23:24.76,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想變得更堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.76,0:23:29.88,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}期望這個聲音總有一天可以傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:32.27,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.27,0:23:35.01,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在風停止的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:39.69,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仰望天空追尋著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.43,0:23:47.02,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}在黎明前散發的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.18,0:23:52.57,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}將會變成彩虹
